data.description: 4 Bed 2 Bath Ranch home with attached garage. Hardwood floors, vinyl windows, Cathedral ceiling, galley kitchen,  newer roof, large covered porch, insulated garage with vented door /workbenches. Central heat and cool. Murphy bed in 4th bedroom to stay. Lovely Ranch home in popular Sherwood District--close to park.
